<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="no">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cisco Packet Tracer Guide</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script src="/frontend.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Cisco Packet Tracer Guide</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="intro">
            <h2>Introduksjon</h2>
            <p>Her får du en rask gjennomgang av hvordan Cisco Packet Tracer fungerer.</p>
            <video controls>
                <source src="video/intro.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Videoen fungerer ikke.
            </video>
        </section>

        <section id="lan-setup">
            <h2>Sette opp et LAN</h2>
            <p>Her lærer du hvordan du setter opp et enkelt LAN med tre maskiner.</p>
            <img src="images/lan-setup.png" alt="LAN-oppsett" class="clickable">
        </section>

        <section id="dns-dhcp">
            <h2>DNS og DHCP</h2>
            <p>Her setter vi opp en DNS- og DHCP-server.</p>
            <img src="images/dns-1.png" alt="DNS-oppsett" class="clickable">
            <img src="images/dns-2.png" alt="DNS-oppsett" class="clickable">
            <img src="images/dns-3.png" alt="DNS-oppsett" class="clickable">
            <img src="images/dns-4.png" alt="DNS-oppsett" class="clickable">
            <p>Her setter vi opp en DHCP server</p>
            <img src="images/dhcp-1.png" alt="DHCP-oppsett" class="clickable">
            <img src="images/dhcp-2.png" alt="DHCP-oppsett" class="clickable">
            <img src="images/dhcp-3.png" alt="DHCP-oppsett" class="clickable">
            <img src="images/dhcp-4.png" alt="DHCP-oppsett" class="clickable">

        </section>

        <section id="glossary">
            <h2>Ordliste</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>LAN:</strong> Local Area Network, et lokalt nettverk.</li>
                <li><strong>DNS:</strong> Domain Name System, oversetter domener til IP-adresser.</li>
                <li><strong>DHCP:</strong> Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol, tildeler IP-adresser automatisk.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

    <div id="lightbox" class="hidden">
        <span class="close">&times;</span>
        <img id="lightbox-img">
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
